* **v[i] = Sim(q[i*feature_dim:(i+1)*feature_dim], q_n[i*feature_dim:(i+1)*feature_dim])
* **d** = FC(v)
* **loss** = MSE(Critic(s,a) + d, Critic(s_n,a_n))
* **loss**.backward()
* **update**(f_c.params) # Adam
* **update**(FC.params) # Adam
* **update**(Critic.params) # Adam
* **f_d.params** = m*f_d.params+(1-m)*f_c.params # momentum averaged ```

